THE IF/THEN FORMULA
Copywriter Craig Clemens explains that his Hook Point creation process
is different for each company and product because they’re all unique.
However, he shares a basic formula that you can use as a starting point to
discover yours. It’s a simple if/then formula: Point out your prospects’
