Effectiveness in interviews and meetings comes from understanding the
perspective of those on the other side of the table. You want to meet their
needs. It’s not about going in and blurting out whatever is on your mind,
so try to actually understand the people on the other side of the table, and
communicate on their level so that you’re on the same page.
