one is better than the other? “Yeah.” Well, you know how at the
end of the day, whatever you drink or eat still needs to appeal to
you? It’s got to taste good; otherwise, it’s medicine, right? “Yeah,
I do know that.” Well, you should try some Dasani. “What
makes it so special?” Dasani is the water that makes your mouth
water.
By doing this exercise, Lupinacci can quickly tell how effective his cam-
